&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üí° &lt;strong&gt;Pro tip:&lt;/strong&gt; Use BOTH &lt;code&gt;ANOMALY_TOTAL_IMPACT_ABSOLUTE&lt;/code&gt; AND &lt;code&gt;ANOMALY_TOTAL_IMPACT_PERCENTAGE&lt;/code&gt; together. Percentage-only alerts fire on a $5 ‚Üí $10 spike (100% increase, but who cares). Absolute-only alerts miss a $1,000 ‚Üí $1,200 spike on a high-spend account. Combining both eliminates noise and catches real problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

