&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cost:&lt;/strong&gt; Anomaly Detection is &lt;strong&gt;free&lt;/strong&gt;. Zero excuse not to have it. üéØ&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


‚ò†Ô∏è Layer 4: Budget Actions ‚Äî The Kill Switch
