&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üí° &lt;strong&gt;Key difference from GCP/Azure:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS Budget Actions are &lt;strong&gt;native&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî no Lambda or Cloud Function required. AWS can directly apply IAM policies, SCPs (in Organizations), or stop EC2/RDS instances. Policy-based actions auto-reset at the start of the next budget period. Instance stop actions do NOT auto-reset ‚Äî instances stay stopped until manually restarted.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

